{"tid":2142565,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天主教區發信學校：促使學生認識《港區國安法》","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T16:26:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1e034b875601eeefb86af56cf43f8ec59db925f3","tid":2142565,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"天主教香港教區向天主教中小學的校監及校長發信。信中指，天主教學校的辦學團體是教育局的長期伙伴，學校應扮演正面角色，並建議學校由新學年起，引導學校教職員團隊，促使學生正確認識《港區國安法》及《國歌法》，培育學生對國民身份認同的正確觀念。<br />\n<br />\n教區亦指要確保學校政策足以防範校園政治化，不讓校園成為任何人單方宣傳政治訊息或訴求的場所。教區建議學校的名義一旦遭人利用，應立即公開澄清，以正視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542257-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542257-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=15ae4948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542257-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5ed32b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542257-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b181bd0897b594c9f2d5ea50ff363c0f7ead3ca9","tid":2142565,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"【飛雲】影一張相等於7000蚊嘅時代來臨了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"50e500fd44590d759b736f38acfe5f5ad942ebe2","tid":2142565,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3250131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3250131&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=ff48739b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F32501